<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />The king rejoices in your strength, Yahweh!</para>

<para style="q1">How greatly he rejoices in the salvation you provide!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />You have given him his heart's desire</para>

<para style="q1">and have not held back the request of his lips.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
